Our Team

Where strategic planning and data-centricity come together to support calculated growth.

Guitar Hero ‚ÄúHero‚Äù

Where in the world he wants to travel to next: Ireland

How he likes his coffee: ‚ÄúI prefer to dump the coffee out and drink Red Bull instead!‚Äù

Color used to describe himself: ‚ÄúBlack and Gold, I can be a huge yinzer at times.‚Äù

Zack is our champion CEO and business development manager who has a lot of experience working for different media companies across print, tv and now digital. Starting Corkboard Concepts meant that he‚Äôll get to work with diverse minds to create something special for all clients.

How he likes his coffee: ‚ÄúBlack Americano that‚Äôs a robust/Arabica blend.‚Äù

Color used to describe himself: ‚ÄúGreen, the standard 24-pack Crayola color. It‚Äôs original, in a not too flashy way.‚Äù

CMO

Spending the first couple years as a digital nomad, Jordan took his ‚Äúmarketing wits‚Äù on a tour of the globe starting online businesses in the US, United Kingdom and Asia.
